OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FIgor Tudor has left his role as
OL,8,FTottenham head coach after just 44
OL,9,Fdays and seven matches in charge.
OL,11,FSpurs made the surprise decision to
OL,12,Fturn to the Croatian after Thomas
OL,13,FFrank was dismissed on February 11.
OL,15,FTudor had never managed in the Premier
OL,16,FLeague, but had experience of sparking
OL,17,Fan upturn in form after mid-season
OL,18,Farrivals and yet suffered five defeats
OL,19,Ffrom seven games, including four in a
OL,20,Frow at the start of his reign.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
