OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FA club statement on Sunday afternoon
OL,8,Fread: "We can confirm that it has been
OL,9,Fmutually agreed for head coach Igor
OL,10,FTudor to leave the club with immediate
OL,11,Feffect.
OL,13,F"Tomislav Rogic and Riccardo Ragnacci
OL,14,Fhave also left their respective roles
OL,15,Fof goalkeeping coach and physical
OL,16,Fcoach.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
