PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774954972
OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,F"We thank Igor, Tomislav and Riccardo
OL,8,Ffor their efforts during the past six
OL,9,Fweeks, in which they worked
OL,10,Ftirelessly. We also acknowledge the
OL,11,Fbereavement that Igor has recently
OL,12,Fsuffered and send our support to him
OL,13,Fand his family at this difficult time.
OL,15,F"An update on a new head coach will be
OL,16,Fprovided in due course."
OL,18,FThe most recent defeat came at home to
OL,19,FNottingham Forest on March 22, prior
OL,20,Fto the international break.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUxD@XO]
