OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FImmediately after that game, the 47-
OL,8,Fyear-old learned his father Mario had
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FTudor's exit leaves Spurs without a
OL,12,Fhead coach heading into the final
OL,13,Fseven games of the Premier League
OL,14,Fseason, with the London club just one
OL,15,Fplace and one point above the
OL,16,Frelegation zone.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
