OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FAssistant Bruno Saltor will lead
OL,8,Ftraining for the players not away on
OL,9,Finternational duty at the moment, the
OL,10,FPress Association understands, with
OL,11,Fthe club aiming to appoint a new head
OL,12,Fcoach in the coming days, in time for
OL,13,Fthe full squad being back together and
OL,14,Fa crucial 10-day preparation period
OL,15,Fahead of the April 12 fixture at
OL,16,FSunderland.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
