OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FFormer Brighton boss Roberto De Zerbi
OL,8,Fand ex-Burnley and Everton manager
OL,9,FSean Dyche are among the bookmakers'
OL,10,Ffavourites to take over, or they could
OL,11,Fturn to Ryan Mason, boyhood Spurs fan
OL,12,Fand player who has twice been
OL,13,Fcaretaker before.
OL,15,FAnother man linked with the role, Adi
OL,16,FHutter, appeared to distance himself
OL,17,Fon Sunday evening from any suggestion
OL,18,Fhe would take up the reins for the run-
OL,19,Fin.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
