OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FIn a statement, quoted by Sky Sport
OL,8,FAustria, the former Monaco boss said:
OL,9,F"In recent days and weeks, I have been
OL,10,Fincreasingly linked with various clubs.
OL,12,F"However, as I already stated
OL,13,Fimmediately after my time at Monaco, I
OL,14,Fwould prefer not to work as a head
OL,15,Fcoach again until the start of the new
OL,16,Fseason at the earliest. My position on
OL,17,Fthis matter has not changed since
OL,18,Fthen."
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
