OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,FTottenham Hotspur Supporters' Trust
OL,8,Fresponded to the news of Tudor's
OL,9,Fdeparture by urging the club to now
OL,10,Fmake a "wise choice" regarding his
OL,11,Freplacement.
OL,13,FIts post on X read: "With thanks to
OL,14,FIgor and his team for their efforts,
OL,15,Fand wishing him and his family time to
OL,16,Fcome to terms with their loss.
OL,18,F"In a season of bad calls, let's hope
OL,19,Fwe now see a wise choice for the
OL,20,Fremainder of the campaign.
OL,26,@rD@HOUrD@TO]uD@UOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
