OL,3,CWhat now for Spurs as Igor Tudor
OL,4,Cleaves as head coach after just seven
OL,5,Cgames?
OL,7,F"Someone who understands the club and
OL,8,Fis up to the task in front of them:
OL,9,Fretaining our Premier League status.
OL,10,FSomeone we can all be proud of and who
OL,11,Fcan bring some much needed success and
OL,12,Fenjoyment to our long suffering
OL,13,Ffanbase."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
